<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:17:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>富士康的目标是与日产合作，而不是收购</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/foxconns-aim-is-cooperation-with-nissan-not-acquisition-2025-02-12/</link><description>富士康董事长杨刘周三表示，该公司的目标是与日本的日产而不是收购。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:37:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/foxconns-aim-is-cooperation-with-nissan-not-acquisition-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>华纳兄弟与中国集团在上海建立“哈利·波特工作室之旅”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-jinjiang-warner-bros-sign-deal-framework-harry-potter-theme-park-shanghai-2025-02-12/</link><description>中国集团周三表示，华纳兄弟公司已同意与金江国际公司在上海开发“哈利·波特工作室之旅”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-jinjiang-warner-bros-sign-deal-framework-harry-potter-theme-park-shanghai-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军确认“常规”台湾海峡运输</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-confirms-routine-taiwan-strait-transit-2025-02-12/</link><description>美国海军在周二证实，其两艘船进行了台湾海峡过境，尽管北京有愤怒的反应，但仍称其为常规。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-navy-confirms-routine-taiwan-strait-transit-2025-02-12/</guid></item><item><title>自从特朗普就职以来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-monitored-us-ship-crossing-taiwan-strait-state-media-reports-2025-02-11/</link><description>自从上个月唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）上任以来，两艘美国海军舰艇本周在台湾海峡敏感的第一个任务中航行，表现出中国的愤怒反应，该行动称这项任务增加了安全风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-monitored-us-ship-crossing-taiwan-strait-state-media-reports-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员说，法案要重新引入美国的投资。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bill-curb-us-investment-china-be-reintroduced-us-lawmaker-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>众议院中国众议院选拔委员会主席周二表示，遏制美国在中国投资的立法将被重新引入国会，并补充说，该法案去年未能通过亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的反对。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 19:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bill-curb-us-investment-china-be-reintroduced-us-lawmaker-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>DeepSeek可能会面临进一步的监管行动，欧盟隐私监督机构说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/deepseek-may-face-further-regulatory-actions-eu-privacy-watchdog-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>欧洲的隐私监督机构周二表示，DeepSeek将来可能会面临民族监管机构的更多行动，强调了集团对廉价中国人工智能创业公司日益普及的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 17:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/deepseek-may-face-further-regulatory-actions-eu-privacy-watchdog-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>信息报告称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-partners-with-alibaba-develop-ai-features-iphone-china-information-reports-2025-02-11/</link><description>苹果公司周二报道说，苹果公司正在与阿里巴巴合作，为中国的iPhone用户推出人工智能功能，并援引一个直接了解该决定的人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 14:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-partners-with-alibaba-develop-ai-features-iphone-china-information-reports-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯的诺尼克尔（Nornickel</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-nornickel-says-it-is-active-talks-china-jv-2025-02-11/</link><description>俄罗斯的诺尼克尔（Nornickel）是精制镍和钯的主要生产国，周二表示，正在就中国的一家合资企业进行积极的谈判，其中包括2025  -  2026年早期金融计划中的潜在投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 11:50:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russias-nornickel-says-it-is-active-talks-china-jv-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>特别报告中国在特朗普削减外国援助时在非洲建立太空联盟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-builds-space-alliances-africa-trump-cuts-foreign-aid-2025-02-11/</link><description>在开罗的郊区，一个尖端的太空实验室应该是非洲第一个生产本土卫星的实验室。但是，进入植物，而不是非洲的形象开始褪色</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 11:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-builds-space-alliances-africa-trump-cuts-foreign-aid-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>尽管收入增长，但中国SMIC的第四季度利润下滑38.4％，遗漏了估计</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-smic-q4-profit-slumps-384-misses-estimates-despite-revenue-growth-2025-02-11/</link><description>中国最大的合同芯片制造商半导体制造商国际公司报告说，第四季度利润同比下降了38.4％。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-smic-q4-profit-slumps-384-misses-estimates-despite-revenue-growth-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国援助冻结风险在北京后院向中国传递影响力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-aid-freeze-risks-handing-influence-china-beijings-backyard-2025-02-11/</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在一月份向柬埔寨最大的Demining组织捐款后，该组织致力于清除华盛顿过去在东南亚的致命遗迹的乡村，该组织从中国宣布了新的资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:12:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-aid-freeze-risks-handing-influence-china-beijings-backyard-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-bubble-tea-firm-mixue-raise-about-500-million-hong-kong-ipo-later-feb-2025-02-11/</link><description>根据对此事的直接了解，中国最大的泡沫茶公司Mixue Group将在2月底开始为其香港首次公开募股，以筹集约5亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-bubble-tea-firm-mixue-raise-about-500-million-hong-kong-ipo-later-feb-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>一月份的近一年中，中国的汽车销售职位最大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-car-sales-january-fall-12-year-earlier-2025-02-11/</link><description>一月份，中国的汽车销售额下降了12％，这是自9月以来的首次下降，是一年来最大的下降，因为汽车制造商在世界上最大的汽车市场上为激烈的竞争做好了努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-car-sales-january-fall-12-year-earlier-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国向印度的煤炭出口预计将由于中国关税而上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-coal-exports-india-expected-rise-due-china-tariffs-2025-02-11/</link><description>五名行业官员说，在中国对美国的能源进口征收关税之后，预计美国将增加对印度的煤炭出口，这可能会侵蚀澳大利亚和俄罗斯在印度市场的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-coal-exports-india-expected-rise-due-china-tariffs-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>百度首席执行官说，尽管DeepSeek的成功，仍然需要更多的人工智能支出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-ceo-says-more-ai-spend-still-needed-despite-deepseeks-success-2025-02-11/</link><description>百度首席执行官罗宾·李（Robin Li）周二表示，尽管DeepSeek挑战了大型AI模型的成本效率，但仍需要对数据中心和云基础设施的投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:39:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-ceo-says-more-ai-spend-still-needed-despite-deepseeks-success-2025-02-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>